<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Darling" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Darling,</orth> subst. one very dear, a favourite: <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 3, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.216" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 216</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.2.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 2, 68</bibl> (Ff <emph>dearling.</emph> cf. <emph>Minion</emph>). <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 44</bibl>. Used of things: <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.110" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.4.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 4, 66</bibl>.<lb />Adjectively: <cit><quote>the d. buds of May,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 18.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 18, 3</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>